Metadata.Title: 1929 Wall Street falls
Metadata.Description:
Suddenly the bank's share price fell to the point where it could not go any lowerBank employees who learned the information chose to fall from the top, lest they and their families be overwhelmed by debts that would take several lifetimes to pay offAuthor: I don't want to make the contract hard, but try to do it with  fall accidentsYou'll understand the fun of it

Exit: Window
